messages.text: Gurrrl you’re getting your party on!!!
Trevor, I think? Idk, I’m v v drunk.
Not as much as you tho.
Hey, I’m happy for you. Glad you’re finally getting over Ryan.
Sorry. Shouldn’t have brought him up.
Dude, it’s fine. I just don’t wanna think about him.
That Brandon guy was feeling you tho???
Urghh, I’m not looking to start anything tonight.
Kk I gotta pee, wanna come with?
Margot, Cas and Robbie are going to DQ! I’m desperate for that good Brownie Batter Blizzard!!!! You Comin’?
How’s it going with the boi?
He’s like, all over you, you gonna be ok?
Just give him your numba and let’s go!!!
I said I’m FINE. I wanna stay.
Don’t get Blizzard on my dress!
And text me when ur home.
Maybe ur just not drunk enough???
I don’t trust these college dudes, let’s just go to DQ okay? I don’t wanna have to like, worry about you all night.
So then don’t worry. It’s fine, they’re all my brother’s friends.
Fine. Whatever. Have a good night.
Robbie just puked up his sundae all over the DQ parking lot!!! So gross!!!!!
I’m fine, leave me alone, I’m tryna make out!!
Wait, Jess! Connor and his crew just showed up at DQ.
He said some of the dudes at the party had like, roofies or something that they were gonna try and slip girls.
Meg, you still at the party
Haha yeah girl, where you at???
At DQ. Have you seen Jess, she’s not answering me.
Yeah, she was with that guy, Trevor. They went upstairs.
Can you look for her please?
Some of the guys have roofies or something…
We’re on our way, have you found her?
Traffic. There was a car accident, we’re stopped.
Okay, apparently they went into the bedroom.
Knock on the door, yell at her!!
Idk, I don’t think so but the music’s really loud.
Get someone to help!! Kick the door in or something!
Okay, Pete and Carl are helping me.
You can’t! We’ll all get arrested for drinking underage.
Okay wait, they got the door open.
Pete’s pulling Trevor off of her.
